{"h8dbdc73bg3434g45a4g9a68ga6fa4f210298": ["Gods, I can finally <i>think!</i>", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "ff59dd24-fce1-4bd5-fbc4-404984d1d6ba"], "h7eee21a9gdd35g441ag803agc299bb2dc4f8": ["Lookit, Derryth! ", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "6c1b4a68-af33-0843-93d1-d24bfea0d7e7"], "hcdd29564g04b4g4bbbg9826g7b367210a3d0": ["What have you done?!", "2b537d2a-14c8-43b3-ab71-d537c925a2a7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "239778f3-1729-98b5-47d0-17fc4fa841fa"], "ha5975532ge0bfg4d11g8b46g212477f12f4b": ["S'matter, woman? I've got my brain back! Smile!", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "3b43a886-2a16-5efa-9c4f-8e6b164c2c18"], "hc8a49b91gc8e6g4c0agb6d2gded7f8e9ff98": ["Derryth, aren't you happy your husband is well again?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "340304b3-84d6-4148-d5fe-802be0f8f0e1"], "h95ac0423g5181g4910g8f7fg09efea5e8c30": ["It's just...", "2b537d2a-14c8-43b3-ab71-d537c925a2a7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "c4d0d6cc-7797-d0de-54a2-72317f5ae7c6"], "h179bab3cgee91g415bgbb7bgb5fcf80bd13a": ["It's just she's lost herself a pack mule and a truffle pig.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "03c6fe7d-da07-ca72-6f2c-86e20595b961"], "h09365ad3ge0e7g4090g8f97g09ec0c87e9fb": ["If you hadn't given me that 'shroom, I'd be her doddering old servant till my dying day.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "8d6a689c-dd48-6864-eae6-2ec1e6bee183"], "hc53ac1d3g6c36g4bd6gb72dg2289663bcf68": ["No bother, though. She'll learn her place again. Won't you, love? Like the good old days.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "1836b506-5af0-0db4-0202-5c0f00358d42"], "haf743c2dg6f56g4c83ga294gc4a10faa889e": ["Come on. Get to packing. We're going home.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "40437c00-ebe4-6bad-b2a0-0f134839c680"], "hc2fadbd8ge2dag494fg9969gf421431d4c05": ["You could stand to speak to your wife with a little more respect, Baelen.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "56a1c504-3fe7-8189-e63e-2272f9b682bd"], "h1d6cc4e7g1314g4dcag84e9gbf4aad83a21b": ["Respect? After she's using me as a pack mule and a truffle pig these past years.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "fdf5c4a1-a487-54a5-fa6b-4dd534147e3f"], "h3c32864eg2199g40b3g8f4ag78466f8c230b": ["<i>Observe the couple silently.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "e16f78e8-c878-a9a4-cdd0-f3ff380d730a"], "h243ab236ge782g463ag81a6g8fba1e5badca": ["<i>Well?</i>", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "26d609dc-a1ec-cdf8-9c7f-5ac40b758bef"], "ha2b35f51g13f0g4568gbd6fga20cabd21329": ["Baelen... it's been a good few years. I need a chance to think.", "2b537d2a-14c8-43b3-ab71-d537c925a2a7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "bf4ef8de-41a7-b17b-e5b0-dfce135dc6f2"], "h11165dd3gaccag422fg8a44g9ff6f363d865": ["Never made a habit of that before. Don't see why you'd start now.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "4db874b8-83bc-55f6-dadd-c042d02117e0"], "ha72bb877g1349g455cg9cacg8eb76c4b61ed": ["Do you remember these last years? Since you've been sick?", "2b537d2a-14c8-43b3-ab71-d537c925a2a7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "ea40d981-1a21-8902-22b7-9ccd3e927689"], "h50063afdg1c44g4749ga8d4ge18a4ff9f700": ["Remember how you used me like a mule?", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "600c7186-6efa-fb07-f194-d9c5eb01809c"], "ha61e10c9g88d2g4e41g84c3g3ed38b293d61": ["I learned <i>that </i>from the best.", "2b537d2a-14c8-43b3-ab71-d537c925a2a7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "c8621bee-51a1-e6a5-c62c-719353f27254"], "h792042a6g5ca0g41c3ga757g5a816121f565": ["Well, the best is back. You'll learn your place again, even if you forgot till now.", "711bd763-780d-4132-9662-3a8a06da6b1b", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MushroomHunter_ThreewayDialogAfterBaelenAteMushroom.html", "102d70ff-be09-ac69-ed07-dad683db41bf"]}